ng a true sense of community online The alumni group is a great place to post job opportunities  find former classmates  share news  learn about upcoming events that are open exclusively to alumni  and post about current issues in engineering or your particular industry Please join us  LinkedIn public page you should see a blue button in the left hand column  so that our updates show up in your LinkedIn news feed  Alternatively  bookmark it and visit whenever you like  This also is a great page to suggest to your professional contacts who may be interested in serving as a partner to UIC Engineering Get Involved Get Involved  n nBack to main content n n n n n n Back to main content Join us on LinkedIn Become a Mentor Volunteer Engineer your own involvement  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Engineering Alumni n         Contact            MWilli   uic edu Social Media Accounts  nFacebook n Facebook UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 